    <h2>Research Interests</h2>
    <p><strong>Methodology:</strong></p>
    <p>Matrix-variate data analysis, Measurement Error, Causal Inference with Network-based Design, Bayesian Analysis, Regression for High-dimensional Data, Experimental Study Designs</p>
    <p><strong>Applications:</strong></p>
    <p>Designing and analyzing complex health studies using innovative statistical methods in HIV research, Brain Imaging, and Oncology</p>
